      "text": "Expanding our tactical reach.\n Our boat crews are the best in the world. As part of #OperationRiverWall, @USCG airboats provide unique capabilities to maximize control and mobility along 260 miles of the Rio Grande River. These platforms allow crews to operatewhere others can’t — reinforcing our layered approach to border security and national defense.\n\nThis is owning the rivers.\n\n#USCG #BorderSecurity #ImmigrationEnforcement #OperationRiverWall #SemperParatus #WeOwnTheRivers @DHSgov @USCGHeartland @TXMilitary @CBP",
